---
// Option 2: Organic Glassmorphism
// Frosted glass panels, fluid shapes, soft gradients, ethereal glow
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>DTP — Organic Glassmorphism</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=General+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=Satoshi:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --deep-navy: #0f172a;
      --violet: #8b5cf6;
      --lavender: #c084fc;
      --glow: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
      --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'General Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--deep-navy);
      color: white;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    
    .heading-font {
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
    }
    
    /* Background effects */
    .bg-gradient {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: 
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 20%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 80%, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    /* Glass card */
    .glass {
      background: var(--glass);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      border-radius: 24px;
    }
    
    /* Header */
    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    }
    
    nav {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: var(--glass);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
    }
    
    .logo {
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .logo-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: var(--violet);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.2); }
    }
    
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      list-style: none;
    }
    
    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--lavender);
    }
    
    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      background: var(--glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--lavender);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, white 0%, var(--lavender) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    
    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .btn {
      font-family: 'General Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 100px;
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--violet) 0%, var(--lavender) 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-color: var(--lavender);
    }
    
    /* Features Section */
    .features-section {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    
    .section-header h2 {
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .section-header p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .features-grid {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card {
      padding: 2.5rem;
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      border-color: var(--violet);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
    }
    
    .feature-card.large {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--violet) 0%, var(--lavender) 100%);
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    
    .feature-card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    /* Process Section */
    .process-section {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .process-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .process-timeline {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      position: relative;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }
    
    .process-timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 40px;
      left: 10%;
      right: 10%;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--violet), var(--lavender));
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    
    .process-step {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .step-circle {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      background: var(--glass);
      border: 2px solid var(--violet);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--lavender);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .process-step:hover .step-circle {
      background: var(--violet);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
    }
    
    .process-step h3 {
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .process-step p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      max-width: 150px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    /* CTA Section */
    .cta-section {
      padding: 8rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .cta-card {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0%, rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.05) 100%);
    }
    
    .cta-card h2 {
      font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .cta-card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    /* Footer */
    footer {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .footer-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }
    
    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
      .feature-card.large {
        grid-column: span 1;
      }
      .process-timeline {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 2rem;
      }
      .process-timeline::before {
        display: none;
      }
      .process-step {
        flex: 0 0 calc(33.333% - 1rem);
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .process-step {
        flex: 0 0 100%;
      }
      .cta-card {
        padding: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-gradient"></div>
  
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-dot"></span>
        Digital Technology Partner
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/services">Approach</a></li>
        <li><a href="/case-studies">Case Studies</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faq">FAQ</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        ✨ AI Development Partner
      </div>
      <h1>AI Simplified</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">We cut through the hype, build AI that works, and prove value through real results — fast, focused, and tailored to you.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Book Discovery Call</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-secondary">Our Process</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why organisations work with us</h2>
        <p>Real engineering, beautiful solutions</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card glass large">
          <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3>Reduced Risk</h3>
          <p>We deliver in stages. You see progress early and avoid big-bang surprises. Every sprint ships working code you can verify.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔐</div>
          <h3>Security by Design</h3>
          <p>Data protection and access controls built in from day one. Security isn't an afterthought.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
          <h3>Reliable Delivery</h3>
          <p>Clear scope, fixed steps, regular check-ins. No scope creep, no surprise invoices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
          <h3>Scales with You</h3>
          <p>Start small, prove value, then roll out without rework. Architecture that grows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass large">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔗</div>
          <h3>Works With Your Tools</h3>
          <p>We integrate with common meeting, messaging, and project platforms. Zero friction onboarding for your team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card glass">
          <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Flexible Engagement</h3>
          <p>Your stack, our cloud, or hybrid. Whatever fits policy and budget.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="process-section">
      <div class="process-container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>Development Journey</h2>
          <p>From idea to production in five proven stages</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-timeline">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-circle">1</div>
            <h3>Discovery</h3>
            <p>Understand the problem, define success</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-circle">2</div>
            <h3>PoC</h3>
